Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　すげえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Isn't this amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.88,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord4\3c&H664A99&\pos(402,388)}Zombies in\NJapan, too!!!
